Overview: MixedMode will generate a binary tree of Filter operators using
mixed-mode SPL/Perl.

1. To build the sample application:
   make

2. To run the sample application:
   ./output/bin/standalone

Notes: 
  - The resulting output is written to the file 'data/Results.txt'. 
  - The output of the preprocessing (via Perl) is 'BinaryTree.spl'. 
    
